BLOG POSTS

what do we want:
  - markdown
  - chronological page
  - only linked titles
  - x amount of posts or titles
  - taxonomy
  
semantics
in page
<<~~BLOG:POSTS:X~~>>
<<~~BLOG:TITLES:X~~>>

in template blogpost
<<~~BLOGPOST:TITLE~~>>
<<~~BLOGPOST:AUTHOR~~>>
<<~~BLOGPOST:TIME~~>>
<<~~BLOGPOST:CONTENT~~>>
